                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation method of sodium 3, 3 '-dithiodipropane sulfonate",
                    "聚二硫二丙烷磺酸钠的制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a preparation method of sodium polydithiodipropane sulfonate, which comprises the following steps: mixing a thioamide compound, 1, 3-propane sultone and a solvent, reacting to obtain 3-sulfur imino propane sulfonic acid, controlling the pH value to be more than 10 by adopting organic alkali, adding an oxidant into the 3-sulfur imino propane sulfonic acid, reacting, and separating to obtain the sodium polydithiodipropane sulfonate. And finally, carrying out vacuum concentration, soaking, washing, suction filtration and drying to obtain the sodium 3, 3 '-dithiodipropane sulfonate. According to the invention, the thioamide compound and the 1, 3-propane sultone are taken as raw materials and are directly sulfonated and oxidized to prepare the sodium dithiodipropane sulfonate, so that a new thought for synthesizing the sodium dithiodipropane sulfonate is provided, the problems existing in the prior art that inorganic matters such as hydrogen sulfide or sulfide salt are taken as raw materials are avoided, and the yield of the sodium dithiodipropane sulfonate is increased. The method has the characteristics of simple process, low energy consumption, less wastewater, high product yield and high effective content, and is beneficial to industrial production of the sodium 3, 3 '-dithiodipropane sulfonate."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种聚二硫二丙烷磺酸钠的制备方法，先将硫代酰胺类化合物、1，3‑丙烷磺酸内酯与溶剂混合，反应得到3‑硫亚胺基丙烷磺酸，再采用有机碱控制pH＞10，向3‑硫亚胺基丙烷磺酸中加入氧化剂进行反应，最后经减压浓缩、泡洗抽滤烘干后得到聚二硫二丙烷磺酸钠。本发明以硫代酰胺类化合物与1，3‑丙烷磺酸内酯为原料直接进行磺化氧化，制得聚二硫二丙烷磺酸钠，提供了一种聚二硫二丙烷磺酸钠的合成新思路，避免了现有技术中采用硫化氢或硫化盐等无机物作为原料存在的问题，减少了聚二硫二丙烷磺酸钠的合成步骤，具有工艺简单、能耗低、废水少、产品的收率高、有效含量高的特点，有利于聚二硫二丙烷磺酸钠的工业化生产。"
                }
            ]
